{"tid":1866820,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【香港人悶起上來可以有幾癲】我想行開下 Remix","createTime":"2020-02-07T02:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T07:03:21.000Z","uid":212944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca6c72688db9d2ccdc47ceeeb4a3ada5b6f3588","tid":1866820,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:10:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BRdq784er3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBRdq784er3s&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWexpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=ed250727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BRdq784er3s</a><br />\n//無乜出街，游走網絡，見到有個姐姐講出我嘅心聲，唉今次真係有誰共鳴。作返首無聊歌，冷靜面對呢個世界。老實講，真係好想行開下，想忘記咗呢個世界呀。/_\\<br />\n做香港人真係好慘慘。希望啟德架郵輪真係真係唔好落客，希望大家身體都健健康康，勿信毒婦散布謠言，無！病！都！要！戴！罩！<br />\n<br />\n儀容方面，由於幾乎沒有出門，著返喺家中穿著多天的米奇老鼠衫同uniqlo運動褲（超舒服）。唔知幾時先可以戴con出街化靚靚展現自信笑容呢？？？<br />\n<br />\nPS：本人目前有足夠使用嘅口罩，歌詞純屬創作（但真係有人無口罩出唔到門口㗎），暫時不用畀口罩我，請關心身邊沒有口罩的朋友，特別是不太會接收網絡資訊，更遑論網購的長者TT//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我笑到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b0ac3b83fbdb0a978b277ceca5323cb52ff4d9","tid":1866820,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:10:29.000Z","msg":"我想行開下 忘記左呢個世界"},{"pid":"2efb776dc9e8e1328bbcaa653f6de2c9d34e9ff9","tid":1866820,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:18:05.000Z","msg":"我想行開下 忘記咗呢個世界"},{"pid":"c51d350475726fa720deb3930f4e85839c4f9372","tid":1866820,"uid":56665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:23:01.000Z","msg":"verse 幾好 夠trap<br />\n如果多D flow 屌柒政府會更HIGH"},{"pid":"94d21f007c6ec5ff4d0f9c86c0f2a1377905dc0a","tid":1866820,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c51d350475726fa720deb3930f4e85839c4f9372","tid":1866820,"ui